{"tid":1619864,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"FYI：啟德新警察東九龍總部大樓年底竣工","createTime":"2019-10-04T08:49:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T04:33:46.000Z","uid":39521,"like":68,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"cf33439b6c0dd6223c68e11b1cdde7624bc5d276","tid":1619864,"uid":39521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:49:26.000Z","msg":"新大樓將在已拆卸的啟德行動基地原址興建，落成後將容納總區總部和各東九龍總區單位，而位於東九龍行動基地的牛頭角分區警署、鐵路警區總部及室內靶場亦會遷往新大樓。<span style=\"color: red;\">工程預計於二〇一九年第四季完工，而大樓則預計於二〇二〇年初啟用。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.police.gov.hk/offbeat/1085/chi/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.police.gov.hk%2Foffbeat%2F1085%2Fchi%2F&d=pX%2F9NM0RDLHEoMpKo%2B7Tofhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=5548e761\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.police.gov.hk/offbeat/1085/chi/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fjpEOL1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfjpEOL1.jpg&h=882807bb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f8d0a62fed5755fd5f8b18e79fca5f3a6a1959d8","tid":1619864,"uid":184229,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:50:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0264aa6e90c3ec73574578d9fc96a146d7c0492","tid":1619864,"uid":130693,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:50:08.000Z","msg":"建築工地？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afea5d27eb1cee8bd31a419106ce8b2572ad29a3","tid":1619864,"uid":290176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:50:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9078cc861802430c7c0f83365a4ee645d845d05","tid":1619864,"uid":69334,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T08:51:09.000Z","msg"